    "Moreover, individuals can sufficiently respond to both the economic and environmental ramifications of climate change and apply knowledge of climate change to their careers, as such knowledge impacts a vast array of fields 10.",
    "In countries like the United States, citizens vote and pay taxes-many of which are relevant to sustainable policies and disaster response plans.",
